\par\pard\plain \tx240\tx720\li720\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Make a light if needed: Making a light tied to this. Separate, first element. Make a \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8216\'91fuel\u8217\'92, shave fur, strike it against his chin and speak a word. THEOREMA Always carry a light at night. - Making everything APART from a knife. Make a flint \endash  strike it against horns \endash  will light. To carry a constant tapre. Add fuel to finger.  Blow to put out fginger. }
