\par\pard\plain \tx240\tx720\li720\fi-720\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 - Sometimes even machines go wrong, she points out. They must be \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8216\'91fixed\u8217\'92, \u8216\'91adjusted\u8217\'92. I never claimed he was perfect. He is still a beest, after all. The first of a new age. There must be some kinks to  work out. Sometimes may misfunction}
